        <abstract>
            <p>JT had not known Lady Lubbock was ill. Will try to persuade her [to change physicians]. Agrees Andrew Clark is best.</p>
            <p>Hooker has survived his crisis [death of his wife].</p>
            <p>St G. J. Mivart’s act is a natural outflow of his character.</p>
        </abstract>
